quran[54]{c,v,t}:
  44,17,"Soni chisimu chene nkanayiche ŵanganyao (Makuraishi) twalinjile mayeso ŵandu ŵa Firiauna, ni jwaichilile Ntenga jwakuchimbichika (Musa)"
  44,18,"(Ni jwatite): “Mumbani achikapolo ŵa Allah (ŵanache ŵa Israila), chisimu une kukwenu ni Ntenga jwakulupichika.”"
  44,19,"“Soni ngasin’dikwesya kwa Allah, chisimu une tinam’bichilile nao umboni wakuonechela.”"
  44,20,“Soni chisimu une nalijuyiye mwa (Allah) M’mbuje gwangu jwali soni M’mbuje gwenu kuti ntakwika mwamusomile maganga.”
  44,21,"“Nambo naga ngankungulupilila, basi mumambalani (ngasimunagasya).”"
  44,22,"(Nambo ŵantendele uwwanga), basi ni jwaŵilasile Ambujegwe (Allah juchitiji): “Chisimu ŵanganyaŵa ni ŵandu ŵakuleŵa, (ndende nao chichi)?”"
  44,23,"(Allah ŵansalile kuti): “Basi ŵigulani ni achikapolo Ŵangu chilo, chisimu ŵanganyammwe tinkuuyidwe.”"
  44,24,"“Soni jilekani mbwani jili mujiŵelelepemo (duu chilekanganile), chisimu ŵanganyao ni asilikali ŵatamisyidwe.”"
  44,25,Ana migunda jilingwa jaŵajilesile ni achitutumule
  44,26,Ni mimela ni pamalo pambone
  44,27,Ni chindimba (chekulungwa) chaŵaliji nkulisengwachisya nacho
  44,28,"Mwele (ni muyaŵelele), ni twapele kuitawalila yalakweyi ŵandu ŵane (ŵanache ŵa Israila)"
  44,29,"Ni nganikwalilila ŵanganyao kwinani ni pasi, nambo soni nganaŵa ŵakupedwa lipesa (lyakutendela toba)"
  44,30,Soni chisimu twajokwele ŵanache ŵa Israila ku ilagasyo yakwalusya
  44,31,"Yakuumila kwa Firiauna, chisimu jwalakwe jwaliji jwakulikwesya, (soni jumpepe) mwa akusumba mpika"
  44,32,Soni twasagwile ŵanganyao (ŵanache ŵa Israila) pa umanyilisi kuipunda iwumbe yosope (yandaŵi jao)
  44,33,Ni twapele ilosyo yayaliji nkati mwakwe mayeso gakuonechela
  44,34,Chisimu ŵanganyaŵa (Makuraishi) akutiji
  44,35,"“Pangali chinechakwe ikaŵeje chiwa chetu chandanda (pechi chatukuwaga chachili chipelela chetu), soni nganituŵa uwwe ŵakwimusyidwa (m’malembe).”"
  44,36,“Basi ikani nao achatati ŵetu (ŵaŵawile kalakala) nam’baga jenumanja nkuŵecheta yakuona (kuti kwana kwimuka m’malembe).”
  44,37,"Ana ŵanganyao (Makuraishi) niŵali ŵambone, kapena ŵandu ŵa Tubba‘i (ŵa ku Yemeni), ni aŵala ŵapaujo pao? Twajonasile (wosope ŵeneo), chisimu ŵanganyao ŵaliji ŵakuleŵa"
  44,38,Soni Uwwe nganitugumba mawunde ni mataka kwisa soni yaili chilikati chakwe mwamasanje
  44,39,"Nganituigumba yele iŵiliyi ikaŵeje mwakuonaonape, nambo ŵajinji mwa ŵanganyao ngakumanyilila"
  44,40,"Chisimu lisiku lyachiilanyo, ni ndema jao wosope ŵene (jajiŵichidwe jakwapela ipotesi)"
  44,41,"Lisiku lyangakamuchisya jwaulongo kwa nnongo n’jakwe chindu chilichose, nambo soni ŵanganyao ngasakulupusyidwa"
  44,42,"Ikaŵeje ŵatachatendela chanasa Allah, chisimu Jwalakwe ni jwali Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwachanasa channope"
  44,43,Chisimu chitela cha Zakkuum
  44,44,Niyakulya ya ŵakulemwa
  44,45,"Yanti mpela ntofu wenyelenyenduche, yaikasemuleje m’matumbo"
  44,46,Chisawu kasemule ka mesi gamoto nnope
  44,47,"(Kuchiŵechetedwa yanti): “Munkwembekanye, ni munkwekwelemechesye pakatikati pa Moto Waukali.”"
  44,48,“Kaneka mpungulile pachanya pa ntwe wakwe ilagasyo ya mesi gamasemule nnope.”
  44,49,"(Tachisalilidwa mwakuchindimbulidwa kuti): “Pasyani, chisimu mmwe ni ŵan’di ŵamachili gakupunda, ŵakuchimbichika nnope.”"
  44,50,“Chisimu ayi ni ayila yamwaliji nkuikaichila.”
  44,51,Chisimu ŵawoga (wakun’jogopa Allah) tachiŵa pamalo gantunjelele
  44,52,"Ku Matimbe ga ku Mbepo, ni achitutumule"
  44,53,"Takawaleje (nguwo sya) silika jwakuŵeŵela ni silika jwakandapalila, (ali atemi) mwakulolegana"
  44,54,"Mwele (ni muyichiŵela), ni tuchalombekasya ni achimmasyeto ŵameso gakulanguka soni gekulungwa mwakusalalila"
  44,55,Takaŵilasyeje mwalakwemo ntundu uliose wa isogosi mwantunjelele
  44,56,"Ngasaja kupasya chiwa mwalakwemo ikaŵeje chiwa chao chandanda (cha pa duniya), ni taakaagoose ku ilagasyo ya Moto Waukali"
  44,57,"Kwa ukoto wakuumila kwa Ambuje ŵenu (Allah), chisimu kwalakweko ni kupunda kwekulungwa nnope"
  44,58,Basi chisimu tujijepepesye (Qur’aniji) mu chiŵecheto chenu (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) kuti ŵanganyao akumbuchile
  44,59,"Basi jembecheyani, chisimu nombe nao (achimakafilio) akwembecheya (sampano tamanyukuche jwakonasika)"
  45,1,Hâ. Mîm
  45,2,"Kutulusyidwa kwa Chitabu (Qur’an) kukuumila kwa Allah, Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwalunda lwakusokoka"
  45,3,Chisimu kumawunde ni petaka kwana ilosyo kwa ŵandu ŵakulupilila (yakulosya kuti Allah apali)
  45,4,"Ni mu kagumbidwe kenu, ni yawumi iliyose yakuulukutaga yaakuijenesya (Allah) iŵele ilosyo kwa ŵandu ŵaakusimichisya (chikulupi chao)"
  45,5,"Ni kupisyangana kwa chilo ni muuusi, ni lisiki (wula) lyatulwisye Allah kuumila kwinani basi ni kusyuchisya nalyo litaka panyuma pakuwa kwakwe, ni kujigalausyagalausya mbungo, iŵele ilosyo kwa ŵandu ŵaakwete lunda"
  45,6,"Galakwega ni ma Ȃya ga Allah gatukunsoomela (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) mwakuonaonape, ana ni nganichi jatajikulupilile panyuma pa (kunkanila) Allah ni ma Ȃya Gakwe"
  45,7,"Ipotesi niyakwe jwalijose jwakulukanya unami nnope, jwasambi syejinji"
  45,8,"Jwaakupikanaga ma Ȃya ga Allah gali nkusoomedwa kukwakwe, kaneka ni jukanganichilaga (kupanganya yakanyisyidwa) mwakulikwesya nti chisawu nganijugapikana (ma Ȃyago), basi mumpani abali ja ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope"
  45,9,"Soni naga ali achimanyi chindu chinechakwe chakuumila m’ma Ȃya Getu, akasachitendelaga chipongwe, ŵanganyao akwete kupata ilagasyo yakwalusya"
  45,10,"Paujo pao pana Jahannama, soni yaŵapanganyisye ngaija kwakamuchisya chilichose, namuno ayila yaŵalitendele kuŵa yakwagosa kunneka Allah, soni akwete kupata ŵanganyao ilagasyo yekulungwa nnope"
  45,11,"Aji (Qur’an) jiŵele chongolo, sano aŵala ŵaagakaanile ma Ȃya ga M’mbuje gwao akwete kupata ilagasyo yakunyalaya ni kupoteka kusyene"